- content_for :title do
  = "Pricing |"
= render partial: 'partials/standard_header'

= javascript_include_tag "pricing"

%section
  .container
    .col-md-12.align-center
      .section-heading
        %br/
        %br/
        %h1.black Quickbox Pricing
        %p.align-center
          QuickBox offers you the lowest price for storage because you only pay for the space you actually use. We've broken pricing down into four categories to help you save. 
  .container.row.pricing-wrapper#pricing-section
    = render partial: 'partials/item_price_box', locals: {icon_class: 'box', item_size: 'small', item_name: 'Small', item_price: 'small', item_description: 'Boxes, tires, bags, or similarly sized objects'}
    = render partial: 'partials/item_price_box', locals: {icon_class: 'bike', item_size: 'medium', item_name: 'Medium', item_price: 'medium', item_description: 'Bikes, chairs, skis, luggage, or coffee tables'}
    = render partial: 'partials/item_price_box', locals: {icon_class: 'couch', item_size: 'large', item_name: 'Large', item_price: 'large', item_description: 'Desks, drawers, TV\'s, armchairs, or small couches'}
    = render partial: 'partials/item_price_box', locals: {icon_class: 'bed', item_size: 'large', item_name: 'XL', item_price: 'extra_large', item_description: 'Dining tables, large bed frames, sectional couches'}
  .container
    %br/
    %br/
    .row
      %h3.dark-gray.align-center.no-margin.light-bold Spring Sale
      %h3.dark-gray.align-center.no-margin Save 15% when you sign up!
    %br/
    .row
      .col-md-6.col-md-offset-3
        .boxed-gray.continue-button.pull-left
          %a.white{"href" => "/signup"}
            %button.btn.btn-primary.blue-bg.blue-bg-hover Get Your Instant Quote

.blue-bar
  %br/ 
  %br/

%section
  .container
    .col-md-12.align-center
      .section-heading
        %br/
        %br/
        %br/
        %h1.black Length of Stay and Volume Discounts
        %p.align-center QuickBox doesn't require minimum contracts, but we do reward customers who store more items longer. 
        %br/
    .col-md-6.align-center
      %h3.black Volume Discount
      /%img{:src => "https://s3.amazonaws.com/storage_rails_app_dev/images/homepage_bg_1.png", :alt => ""}/
      %p.align-center.medium-text Storing a lot of stuff? Perfect because with QuickBox the more you store the more you save. We instantly adjust your monthly rate based on how much you store. Even if you add more to your storage months later we'll cut your rates resulting in more savings to you!
    .col-md-6.align-center
      %h3.black Length of Stay Discount
      /%img{:src => "https://s3.amazonaws.com/storage_rails_app_dev/images/homepage_bg_1.png", :alt => ""}/
      %p.align-center.medium-text Storing for more than a few months? QuickBox automatically reduces your monthly rate based on the length of your stay. So stay a month or stay many, we'll make sure you have the lowest rate possible!

    .col-md-4.col-md-offset-4
      %br/
      .boxed-gray.continue-button.pull-left
        %a.white{"href" => "/signup"}
          %button.btn.btn-primary.blue-bg.blue-bg-hover Sign Up Now

.blue-bar
  %br/ 
  %br/

%section
  .container
    = render partial: 'partials/benefits_section'
    %br/
    %br/
    .col-md-4.col-md-offset-4
      %br/
      .boxed-gray.continue-button.pull-left
        %a.white{"href" => "/signup"}
          %button.btn.btn-primary.blue-bg.blue-bg-hover Sign Up Now


= render :partial => 'partials/footer'
